{"tid":1515834,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[防具篇] 家庭用品防狼工具","createTime":"2019-08-29T10:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T16:33:26.000Z","uid":68216,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6a14327dc55f17db49241f251f58899e3003c2f0","tid":1515834,"uid":68216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:28:41.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲 依排出街夜晚行街散步 總係有啲痴線佬跟住尾、打人 甚至攞刀斬人 我哋每次行動都冇可能好多人一齊行 <br />\n<br />\n咁係依個時候我哋就需要自己好好保護自己 由於香港係當防狼噴霧係攻擊性武器 所以就唔可以攜帶出街啦 <br />\n<br />\n但係有好多野係屋企都可以拎住傍身 而且又唔會怕俾人當係攻擊性武器<br />\n<br />\n白胡椒粉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8kRVLH0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8kRVLH0.jpg&h=00414d1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好處係易於攜帶、各大超市有售、唔係攻擊性武器、俾人周到都可以話煮飯用<br />\n<br />\n當遇到痴線佬極端時候 就擰開個蓋 一潑落去 可以立即驅趕、癱瘓目標<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尤其是夜晚出去嘅巴絲 記得每人配備一個啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同場加影<br />\n<br />\n[防具篇] <br />\n【突發】新裝備解鎖 唔怕俾黑社會圍！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1433858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1433858</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[國際文宣篇]<br />\n全部國際文宣既方向完全錯哂 外國睇完根本唔會有行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1493858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1493858</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2a90bde4e8d7841b4ef88ec99eb351a42e160406","tid":1515834,"uid":68216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:37:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6827ff0a419078233d9f2b76ea0f97ecca58a28c","tid":1515834,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:55:04.000Z","msg":"唉 白色恐怖"},{"pid":"ab6ddcb657e0b5dfdef1e5f9c73bba670546a200","tid":1515834,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6827ff0a419078233d9f2b76ea0f97ecca58a28c","tid":1515834,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:55:04.000Z","msg":"唉 白色恐怖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:06:13.000Z","msg":"唉都冇用"},{"pid":"7493eec1238c444763c8678b7bccfe047ba044ba","tid":1515834,"uid":216253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:47:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />　呢排咁多蚊又成日落雨 帶支蚊怕水同遮出街都好正常啊"},{"pid":"b2798bd267769f390e3dbbecb15f32d09eea43a8","tid":1515834,"uid":68216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:18:21.000Z","msg":"岩丫 係屋企拎得起手既野就盡量諗下點運用黎保護自己<br />\n<br />\n推到個個都提高保護自己嘅意識"},{"pid":"01eea23bd9ec15072b977c46b60c43912b63dd9e","tid":1515834,"uid":266962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:33:26.000Z","msg":"推"}]}